    <a href="/guides/cleaning-product-storage-what-to-check-before-buying-cabinets-or-caddies/">cleaning product storage guide</a>,
    with related utility-room planning in <a href="/categories/laundry/">Laundry</a> and the{" "}
    <a href="/guides/lower-waste-laundry-essentials/">lower-waste laundry guide</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    For the broader pet setup, continue with <a href="/guides/pet-essentials-for-australian-homes/">pet essentials</a>,
    <a href="/guides/pet-friendly-home-products-for-australian-households/">pet-friendly home products</a>{" "}
    or the <a href="/guides/new-puppy-essentials/">new puppy guide</a>.
  </p>

